# CLAUDE.md

This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.

## Project Overview

**weather_alarm** (날씨 알람 프로젝트) - A weather alarm project.

## Current State

This is a new repository with no implementation yet. As the codebase develops, this file should be updated with:

- Build, test, and development commands
- Architecture overview and design patterns
- Key modules and their responsibilities
- Configuration and environment setup
- Integration points and external dependencies

## Development Guidelines

When implementing this project:
- Consider the target platform (mobile app, web service, IoT device, etc.)
- Define the weather data source and API integration strategy
- Establish the alarm/notification mechanism
- Plan the user configuration and preference storage
